Data Access Library (DAL) - ReleaseSteps
========================================

- check/update ChangeLog and KnownIssues
- check/bump version numbers of updated LOFAR file formats in DAL/dal/lofar/*_File.cc
- git pull, build and run test suite on the LOFAR cluster head node
- bump version number in DAL/CMakeLists.txt and push to github
- push final user manual and doxygen to github webpage (remote branch 'gh-pages')
- create git tag 2.y.z and push to github
    git tag -m "Tag version 2.y.z" V2.y.z
    git push --tags
- (ask admin to) install new version on the LOFAR cluster
- notify users with release message:
    - mailing lists: nextgen-astrodata@astron.nl, lofar-cep@astron.nl
    - LUS forum: http://lus.lofar.org/forum/

